    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >踏入怪兽料理的世界！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一位可爱的怪兽厨师，展开一场独特的烹饪冒险。你的美食之旅从餐车开始，穿越沙漠、繁华都市，为怪兽顾客提供美味佳肴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/4bfd0bd111b6d87a61d32a516f286747.poster.avif?t=1765375044\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/4bfd0bd111b6d87a61d32a516f286747.webm?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/4bfd0bd111b6d87a61d32a516f286747.mp4?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小心！你可能会成为下一道菜！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场紧张刺激的烹饪挑战中，时间是你的最大敌人！怪兽顾客脾气暴躁，你必须快速行动，否则你自己就会上餐桌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/8d31ec4272cdad560e7ae822972e1954.poster.avif?t=1765375044\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/8d31ec4272cdad560e7ae822972e1954.webm?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/8d31ec4272cdad560e7ae822972e1954.mp4?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人游戏，或与好友本地/在线合作！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友组队，快速满足挑剔的顾客！支持本地或在线合作模式，但别拖慢节奏，否则你可能会变成食材！（本地合作需要控制器。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/12e61e6f265bf2546b08a2361b9c42b3.poster.avif?t=1765375044\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/12e61e6f265bf2546b08a2361b9c42b3.webm?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/12e61e6f265bf2546b08a2361b9c42b3.mp4?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >狩猎食材，制作怪奇美食！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各地的奇异生物，挑战传统口味！你需要在街头捕鼠、公园抓鸽子、甚至在下水道里寻找蟑螂作为食材。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/cd5e0dad2728379fd704d0c60a55a47f.poster.avif?t=1765375044\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/cd5e0dad2728379fd704d0c60a55a47f.webm?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/cd5e0dad2728379fd704d0c60a55a47f.mp4?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种烹饪方式与食材组合！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的烹饪技巧精心切割、油炸、烘焙、烹煮这些奇特食材，让你的移动厨房发挥最大潜力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/61632992db1245ede54897c38c1736c7.poster.avif?t=1765375044\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/61632992db1245ede54897c38c1736c7.webm?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/61632992db1245ede54897c38c1736c7.mp4?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级你的餐车！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着关卡推进，你的餐车将不断升级，解锁更多烹饪设备，应对日益严苛的挑战。游戏包含 20 个关卡，横跨 4 种不同环境，每个区域都有独特的氛围和车辆设定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/dd29e644e7915b02242c9cb4d62d7665.poster.avif?t=1765375044\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/dd29e644e7915b02242c9cb4d62d7665.webm?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021850/extras/dd29e644e7915b02242c9cb4d62d7665.mp4?t=1765375044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在最多 4 人合作模式中挺过疯狂挑战！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全新的生存模式中度过日益艰难的每一天，支持单人游戏或最多 4 名厨师的本地与在线合作。升级你的餐车，对抗不断增加的压力，并一起努力活到退休！</p>",
